Package: modelVis
Title: Interactive Diagnostics Dashboards for Stock Assessment
    Models
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R:
    person("Samuel", "Johnson", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "sdnjohnson@landmarkfisheries.com")
Author: Samuel Johnson [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Samuel Johnson <sdnjohnson@landmarkfisheries.com>
Description: Generates interactive HTML flexdashboard reports
    for stock assessment model diagnostics. Converts raw model
    output into standardised data structures and renders
    navigable dashboards with plotly visualisations. Currently
    supports sableOpMod with planned support for SISCA models.
